Maintainer: Paschalis Chatzopoulos <paschatzop@gmail.com>
Description: 
    Package that provides functions to calculate ecosystem coupling metrics. This
    is a work in progress and the package will be updated with more functions.
    Next major update will include functions to build null models and calculate
    different types of coupling metrices (coupling, decoupling, anticoupling).
